  "body": "### Description\n\nFail native integration tests if certain metrics (e.g. binary size, used classes/methods, RSS used at build-time and run-time) are outside a given range. Ideally we would like time-sensitive metrics included as well but these are expected to be significantly different across different HW.\r\n\r\nSuch an addition would allow us to detect performance regressions early on.\n\n### Implementation ideas\n\nSet the expected ranges (min, max) for each metrics in a file in each integration test directory and create the test harness to retrieve these metrics and compare them with the given range.  ",
